---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = "1 March 2025";
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer — SolanaForensics" description="Disclaimer for SolanaForensics.com">
  <div style="height: 70px;"></div>
  <section style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 5rem 0 4rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tag">// Legal</div>
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="mono" style="color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.78rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="container legal-body">
      <h2>Forensic Intelligence Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The blockchain intelligence outputs, wallet analyses, transaction traces, and reports produced by SolanaForensics are provided for investigative and informational purposes only. They do not constitute legal advice, and should not be relied upon as the sole basis for legal or enforcement action.</p>
      <h2>No Legal Advice</h2>
      <p>Nothing on this website or within the Platform constitutes legal advice. For legal guidance, consult a qualified legal professional in your jurisdiction.</p>
      <h2>Accuracy of Blockchain Data</h2>
      <p>While we take care to ensure the accuracy of on-chain data and analysis, blockchain data is inherently complex and subject to interpretation. Risk scores, entity labels, and analytical conclusions are probabilistic assessments, not definitive determinations of guilt or liability.</p>
      <h2>Third-Party Data</h2>
      <p>The Platform integrates data from third-party sources including Helius, Arkham Intelligence, Solscan Pro, and CoinGecko. We are not responsible for the accuracy or availability of third-party data.</p>
      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Clavestra Intel accepts no liability for decisions made or actions taken on the basis of Platform outputs. Users are solely responsible for ensuring that their use of the Platform complies with applicable laws and professional standards.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.legal-body { max-width: 760px; padding: 4rem 0 6rem; }
.legal-body h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 0.875rem; color: var(--text); padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.legal-body h2:first-child { border-top: none; padding-top: 0; margin-top: 0; }
.legal-body p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; }
</style>
